      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and retaining its original factory luster. An uncompromising choice for the discerning enthusiast, it represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled integrity and mechanical excellence.",
